{"tid":407590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康請林鄭向京轉達：港人只為爭取民主，不是顛覆國家","createTime":"2017-09-20T14:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T14:36:57.000Z","uid":41351,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"23f4e5899f43743b7d93381e9b1ec20cdaebfbe7","tid":407590,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:09:48.000Z","msg":"彭定康:香港討論民主不代表顛覆國家政權  <br />\n        前港督彭定康繼續第二日訪港行程. 他出席香港民促會午餐會發表演說時表示, 特首林鄭月娥需要團結社會,不要讓中聯辦經常干預香港事務, 向北京政府清楚解釋香港討論民主, 不代表顛覆國家政權.<br />\n        彭定康又指, 不認同港獨, 但認同香港應該爭取民主自由, 認為2014年佔中運動會影響香港於2047年的命運.他寄語在獄中服刑的香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒等人, 指他們必須要堅守信念, 因為他們所代表的價值可以令世界變得更好.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20170920162337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20170920162337&d=ZVdzScmQ96ORb1aWjSxf7C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=cb42c4d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20170920162337</a>"},{"pid":"d6d20c2e002cc5f9eb6fcad7d2c8db069b9a9a9a","tid":407590,"uid":45518,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"我只想香港獨立，從冇諗過顛覆中共。我反而希望中共幫手鎖住班中國人"},{"pid":"98272e4739bf7dc508af97c7fad156f09ef9d3e3","tid":407590,"uid":42921,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"彭定康太天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71400c6ea8fd3001e13a76cfb886a9bff4f767a6","tid":407590,"uid":31389,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:28:52.000Z","msg":"爭取民主咪即係顛覆國家"},{"pid":"9535dde1b33227fc7485515a9d84fdb00d7cd85a","tid":407590,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"其實佢都算係咁,佢咁嘅身份同年紀大可以拍下屎忽當唔知,更甚可以奶下共幫英國傾啲生意返嚟"},{"pid":"4bd704005b707b42ee15b013f59b5f86ffad9825","tid":407590,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"<im